<plot>Phillis and Mark are two souls trapped in limbo. Two servants in 1755 Boston occupying an ominous and dynamic landscape, struggle to make sense of the memories of their past lives. Who were Phillis and Mark? What was life for them like in 1755 Boston? An experimental film exploring the nature of collective memory and local history.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?088522</url></doc>
